         standard_metadata.egress_spec = port;
         hdr.ethernet.srcAddr = hdr.ethernet.dstAddr;
         hdr.ethernet.dstAddr = dstAddr;
-        hdr.ipv4.ttl = hdr.ipv4.ttl - 1;
+    }
+
+    action mark_dscp() {
+	hdr.ipv4.diffserv = 46;
+    }
+
+    action decrease_ttl() {
+	if (hdr.ipv4.ttl > 1) {
+	    hdr.ipv4.ttl = hdr.ipv4.ttl - 1;
+	} else {
+	    drop();
+	    return();
+	}
     }
 
     table ipv4_lpm {
@@ -113,7 +125,19 @@ control MyIngress(inout headers hdr,
 
     apply {
         if (hdr.ipv4.isValid()) {
-            ipv4_lpm.apply();
+            if (hdr.ipv4.protocol == 1) {
+		//ICMP
+		mark_dscp();
+	    } else if (hdr.ipv4.protocol == 6) {
+		 //TCP
+		 drop();
+		 return;
+	    } else if (hdr.ipv4.protocol == 17) {
+		 //UDP
+		 decrease_ttl();
+	    }
+
+	    ipv4_lpm.apply();
         }
     }
 }
